{
  "reader_我的郁金香小姐__0": {
    "taskId": "d3a527c4-4364-43ef-8245-61a5b2cfa593",
    "phase": "done",
    "segments": [
      {
        "index": 0,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "这又是一个下了班后的傍晚，江桥乘着86路车回到了郁金香路，江桥家就住在站台50米之外的一个小弄堂里，环境虽算不上太好，但胜在清静，尤其在去年巷子里多了一间名为＂心情＂的咖啡店后，使得周边办公楼里许多厌恶了聒噪和快节奏生活的白领们都找到了这里，然后在夜晚来临前喝一杯咖啡，仿佛只是在这里听一首轻音乐、失神的待一会儿，便会丢掉一切在世俗里惹上的烦恼。",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/fdab8ef1-2eb4-42fa-bb70-aceb92ce1ead.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 1,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "进了弄堂，江桥便摘掉了脖子上的领带，将其挂在肩上向咖啡店走去，江桥约了陈艺下班后在这里谈合作的事情。",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/c45bcf0a-328a-4300-a775-63db7a2ac372.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 2,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "咖啡店很小，除了吧台旁边的一排长椅，仅有的几个座位全部靠着窗户，而正在里面消费的客人都很沉默，似乎没有人愿意对着一杯咖啡说破生活里的脆弱，久而久之这种氛围便成了这间咖啡店独特的标签，尽管巷子很深不易被发现，但它也靠着这个特色，竟然就这么一直生存了下来。",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/79f6cf68-3fd1-43ce-b810-c964105bcb2d.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 3,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "陈艺已经在我之前到了咖啡店，只见她的头发盘的很整齐，脸上的妆也没卸，身上则穿着一件很得体的白色气质女装，估计是刚下了节目，便来赴我的约了。",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/ec808311-8d3e-4706-9949-d9e8cd754818.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 4,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "江桥将公文包很随便的往桌子上一扔，在她的对面位置坐了下来，开口问道：",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/8f82ae7d-378c-4740-a1c7-963b9d1076df.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 5,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "江桥",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "＂你最近忙啥呢，我都好几天没见着你了。＂",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": "钟离",
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": {
          "neutral": {
            "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          }
        },
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/9899849e-8bae-4c8e-b6fd-9a43397df6b5.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 6,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "陈艺",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "＂我们台有个真人秀节目在杭州那边拍摄，我过去出差了几天。＂",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "4cea6ef9-cd75-4f90-afdb-4d1531e0a448",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": "刻晴",
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": {
          "angry": {
            "id": "d0fc651f-c4c3-4914-b7fe-8c898867423d",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "neutral": {
            "id": "4cea6ef9-cd75-4f90-afdb-4d1531e0a448",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "melancholy": {
            "id": "39a8e2ba-7220-42ea-84ae-1e01808c5c3d",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "happy": {
            "id": "d1707117-4a36-48a7-b8ce-792b7a26c0b5",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "disgusted": {
            "id": "b5ce78c8-acbd-4fba-a21c-914a295ccfce",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          }
        },
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/ca6734ab-4cae-42ff-b140-6b31d97f5989.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 7,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "江桥",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "＂哦。＂",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": "钟离",
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": {
          "neutral": {
            "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          }
        },
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/a23f852f-3d86-4d2e-a055-f532ea7fde00.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 8,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "江桥应了一声，随即又喊来服务员要了一瓶啤酒。",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/da308636-0682-482c-a112-69d023b54de0.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 9,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "虽然今天江桥约陈艺是为了谈工作，可是这个世界上却没有比他们更熟悉的人了。他们都是南京雨花台区人，更是一起在这条弄堂里长大的青梅竹马，而在她没有去北京上中国传媒大学之前，他们每天过着抬头不见低头见的生活。后来，江桥进了一家婚庆公司做婚庆策划；她呢，比江桥要优秀太多了！大学毕业后，便进了本地电视台工作，现在已经是一个很有名气的主持人了。",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/20c38a55-9587-4a1b-9b9e-9adc4885d776.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 10,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "一瓶啤酒就这么被江桥当作解暑的饮料给喝完，却迟迟没有开口说起工作的事情，江桥就是想借机和陈艺多待会儿，这些年他们已经不像从前那么亲近了。",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/6b4e4b88-cf51-4dd0-ad55-766acccb49fb.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 11,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "陈艺盯着江桥看了一会儿，终于带着好奇问道：",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/587a0d6b-5938-4c87-9659-b1249533e35c.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 12,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "陈艺",
        "emotion": "surprised",
        "text": "＂江桥，你不是约我出来谈合作嘛，怎么一句话也不说了？＂",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "4cea6ef9-cd75-4f90-afdb-4d1531e0a448",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": "刻晴",
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": {
          "angry": {
            "id": "d0fc651f-c4c3-4914-b7fe-8c898867423d",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "neutral": {
            "id": "4cea6ef9-cd75-4f90-afdb-4d1531e0a448",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "melancholy": {
            "id": "39a8e2ba-7220-42ea-84ae-1e01808c5c3d",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "happy": {
            "id": "d1707117-4a36-48a7-b8ce-792b7a26c0b5",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "disgusted": {
            "id": "b5ce78c8-acbd-4fba-a21c-914a295ccfce",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          }
        },
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/0466afac-0359-45b9-a9d9-2eaf1c983e30.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 13,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "江桥",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "＂谈合作之前我想先问你一件事儿。＂",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": "钟离",
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": {
          "neutral": {
            "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          }
        },
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/48285f67-adcc-49be-92a0-adb1377cddc5.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 14,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "陈艺",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "＂你问呗。＂",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "4cea6ef9-cd75-4f90-afdb-4d1531e0a448",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": "刻晴",
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": {
          "angry": {
            "id": "d0fc651f-c4c3-4914-b7fe-8c898867423d",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "neutral": {
            "id": "4cea6ef9-cd75-4f90-afdb-4d1531e0a448",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "melancholy": {
            "id": "39a8e2ba-7220-42ea-84ae-1e01808c5c3d",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "happy": {
            "id": "d1707117-4a36-48a7-b8ce-792b7a26c0b5",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "disgusted": {
            "id": "b5ce78c8-acbd-4fba-a21c-914a295ccfce",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          }
        },
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/ad6ededa-9a05-4697-9348-ec75efb32f9b.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 15,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "江桥",
        "emotion": "happy",
        "text": "＂想我江桥从小就阳光帅气，还乐于助人、三观向上、德智体美劳样样是标兵，深得老师们喜欢，更是年年被学校评为优秀红领巾，所以……我想问你：当这么多优点很不公平的集中在我一个人身上时，有没有那么一霎那让你心动过，然后偷偷暗恋我，把我当成你梦中的白马王子？＂",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": "钟离",
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": {
          "neutral": {
            "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          }
        },
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/9688f1de-32b8-4838-a722-1e21402e1c70.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 16,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "陈艺",
        "emotion": "disgusted",
        "text": "＂没有……你能不能别每次一见面就像和我说脱口秀似的，说好的谈合作呢？＂",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "b5ce78c8-acbd-4fba-a21c-914a295ccfce",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": "刻晴",
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": {
          "angry": {
            "id": "d0fc651f-c4c3-4914-b7fe-8c898867423d",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "neutral": {
            "id": "4cea6ef9-cd75-4f90-afdb-4d1531e0a448",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "melancholy": {
            "id": "39a8e2ba-7220-42ea-84ae-1e01808c5c3d",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "happy": {
            "id": "d1707117-4a36-48a7-b8ce-792b7a26c0b5",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "disgusted": {
            "id": "b5ce78c8-acbd-4fba-a21c-914a295ccfce",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          }
        },
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/41aafe12-ba50-484c-8d82-d4b043dd8297.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 17,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "江桥",
        "emotion": "happy",
        "text": "＂得了吧，那么多姑娘喜欢我，你肯定是淹没在她们非我不嫁的意念中感到自卑了。＂",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": "钟离",
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": {
          "neutral": {
            "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          }
        },
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/8d3a408b-3507-439d-8cda-947a83e00643.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 18,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "陈艺不愿意陪江桥无聊，又端起咖啡喝了一口，然后望着巷尾的那两棵很茂盛的梧桐树。",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/ad8b5fe0-3f0b-4a64-becb-c1a1867e93ba.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 19,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "江桥",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "＂好、好、好……咱们谈合作还不行嘛。＂",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": "钟离",
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": {
          "neutral": {
            "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          }
        },
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/4fd4274f-a251-450a-b130-6d33c8fcc231.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 20,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "陈艺没什么情绪的看着江桥，在她眼里江桥是基本上不会一本正经的带着工作精神和她聊天的。",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/a877689c-a899-45c5-8cbd-2ffb6738b43d.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 21,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "江桥坐直了身子，终于正色说道：",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/12e92bd9-98e5-4530-939e-6ba66fc23c72.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 22,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "江桥",
        "emotion": "happy",
        "text": "＂我们公司昨天接了个大客户的婚礼，对方指明要你担任主持，出场费是6万，这是我帮你和老板争取的……呵呵，是不是我江桥偶尔也能做几次靠谱的事情？＂",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": "钟离",
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": {
          "neutral": {
            "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          }
        },
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/2d04234c-cdaf-4087-93f8-33579dbbd6ba.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 23,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "说完这些，江桥心里很高兴，因为这些年江桥在她的世界里太没有存在感了，可是却没有能力为她做点儿什么，这次虽然也算不上是帮忙，但至少证明江桥还算是有点作用的，因为老板起初只愿意给出5万的出场费，而陈艺之前主持一场商业活动也差不多就是这个价格。",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/063db873-93d6-475d-969b-68803f0474ca.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 24,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "陈艺",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "＂江桥，是这样的，最近台里下达了通知，要严整不正之风，严禁体制内的主持人出去接私活，我是签了承诺书的，所以这场婚礼的主持我不能接。＂",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "4cea6ef9-cd75-4f90-afdb-4d1531e0a448",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": "刻晴",
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": {
          "angry": {
            "id": "d0fc651f-c4c3-4914-b7fe-8c898867423d",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "neutral": {
            "id": "4cea6ef9-cd75-4f90-afdb-4d1531e0a448",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "melancholy": {
            "id": "39a8e2ba-7220-42ea-84ae-1e01808c5c3d",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "happy": {
            "id": "d1707117-4a36-48a7-b8ce-792b7a26c0b5",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "disgusted": {
            "id": "b5ce78c8-acbd-4fba-a21c-914a295ccfce",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          }
        },
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/6c9529d9-911c-488d-8f93-b9127fca0a14.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 25,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "江桥心里顿时不高兴了起来，说道：",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/d78299b1-4444-4870-b7ae-2ef78e29aeaf.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 26,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "江桥",
        "emotion": "angry",
        "text": "＂这是公司的事情，也是我的任务指标，我的忙你也不帮吗？＂",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": "钟离",
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": {
          "neutral": {
            "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          }
        },
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/8be798a2-2ee1-45ce-8b3e-53fe60668cec.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 27,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "陈艺",
        "emotion": "sad",
        "text": "＂我不是不帮，是台里下达了这样的通知，我也没办法的呀。＂",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "4cea6ef9-cd75-4f90-afdb-4d1531e0a448",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": "刻晴",
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": {
          "angry": {
            "id": "d0fc651f-c4c3-4914-b7fe-8c898867423d",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "neutral": {
            "id": "4cea6ef9-cd75-4f90-afdb-4d1531e0a448",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "melancholy": {
            "id": "39a8e2ba-7220-42ea-84ae-1e01808c5c3d",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "happy": {
            "id": "d1707117-4a36-48a7-b8ce-792b7a26c0b5",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "disgusted": {
            "id": "b5ce78c8-acbd-4fba-a21c-914a295ccfce",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          }
        },
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/7acd386d-306b-4309-9410-d803823e3ce5.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 28,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "江桥的自尊心忽然受挫，觉得自己的沾沾自喜有点可笑，语调也提高了几分：",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/1864a9f5-e7e2-4b31-bce7-aa9cd4527f33.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 29,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "江桥",
        "emotion": "angry",
        "text": "＂陈艺，别让我觉得你太没有人情味，行吗？＂",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": "钟离",
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": {
          "neutral": {
            "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          }
        },
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/f945b49f-c1c7-4381-9f89-d50e23c8b21b.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 30,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "陈艺看着江桥，没有言语，似乎用沉默再次告诉江桥，这个忙她就是不帮，没得商量。",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/59b8eefc-ec1e-459b-b38c-fb710b91a126.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 31,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "江桥心中上火的厉害，又逼着问道：",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/79923dc3-de34-4194-9d1f-abf24689d759.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 32,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "江桥",
        "emotion": "angry",
        "text": "＂我现在很不高兴，你给句痛快话，这场婚礼你到底能不能主持？＂",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": "钟离",
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": {
          "neutral": {
            "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          }
        },
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/2d6e4ae4-63dd-489b-a7ed-b596a07fe14b.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 33,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "陈艺",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "＂江桥，你能不能成熟一点，我既然和台里签了承诺书，那我就要有契约精神，而且工作上的事情，我们最好不要带着私人感情去聊，这样大家才都不会尴尬、为难。＂",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "4cea6ef9-cd75-4f90-afdb-4d1531e0a448",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": "刻晴",
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": {
          "angry": {
            "id": "d0fc651f-c4c3-4914-b7fe-8c898867423d",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "neutral": {
            "id": "4cea6ef9-cd75-4f90-afdb-4d1531e0a448",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "melancholy": {
            "id": "39a8e2ba-7220-42ea-84ae-1e01808c5c3d",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "happy": {
            "id": "d1707117-4a36-48a7-b8ce-792b7a26c0b5",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "disgusted": {
            "id": "b5ce78c8-acbd-4fba-a21c-914a295ccfce",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          }
        },
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/b14351a7-2ce3-4776-958e-292174d486be.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 34,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "江桥",
        "emotion": "angry",
        "text": "＂好、你字字珠玑、句句在理，我江桥就是个大草包，这事儿就算我不成熟、没有契约精神行了吧？＂",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": "钟离",
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": {
          "neutral": {
            "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          }
        },
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/f65be597-086a-4fbd-a82f-c88e25751814.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 35,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "陈艺",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "＂反正我把我的难处都和你说了，你要和我置气、耍情绪，那我也没有办法。＂",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "4cea6ef9-cd75-4f90-afdb-4d1531e0a448",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": "刻晴",
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": {
          "angry": {
            "id": "d0fc651f-c4c3-4914-b7fe-8c898867423d",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "neutral": {
            "id": "4cea6ef9-cd75-4f90-afdb-4d1531e0a448",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "melancholy": {
            "id": "39a8e2ba-7220-42ea-84ae-1e01808c5c3d",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "happy": {
            "id": "d1707117-4a36-48a7-b8ce-792b7a26c0b5",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          },
          "disgusted": {
            "id": "b5ce78c8-acbd-4fba-a21c-914a295ccfce",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          }
        },
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/9be7a942-d870-4f2a-88dc-2d504a3a5403.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 36,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "江桥",
        "emotion": "angry",
        "text": "＂陈艺你给我听好了，我江桥今天就和你说一句狂话，你不主持没关系，反正混出名声的主持人也不是你一个，这6万块钱我送的出去，我要再和你提这件事情，你就是我奶奶，我是你孙子！＂",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": "钟离",
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": {
          "neutral": {
            "id": "857e60db-4894-4c6b-9de3-f95d9e5ed8bf",
            "mode": 1,
            "emoWeight": 0.65
          }
        },
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/61e45d3c-d9cc-4be0-b4d3-9cdc5be0968b.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 37,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "离开那间叫＂心情＂的咖啡店，江桥所有的心情都瞬间都没了，只剩下一肚子发泄不出去的憋屈，江桥很难过、真的很难过，更觉得自己傻逼到有些可笑，没有今晚这一幕之前，江桥还真把自己太当回事儿，以为在陈艺心中有着很重的分量，结果却抵不上一份签了字的承诺书。",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/48202b72-014a-4352-b94e-c4ba2aa1b56e.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 38,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "江桥就这么站在弄堂里，看着陈艺的身影离开了咖啡店，她在青石铺成的小路上伴随着夜色一步步消失在了江桥的视线中，江桥有些恍惚，好似她的身影还弥留在巷子的深处，就像一个风华绝代的女人用穿着旗袍的背影惊艳着上个世纪30年代的老南京……",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/de5399e1-3860-40e2-948e-8871c5579593.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 39,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "陈艺就是这个样子，从小生活在知识分子家庭的她，学音乐、学舞蹈、学画画，学出了一身才艺，也学出了不动怒的大家闺秀性格，可这些都成了今天他们无法碰触的距离，因为江桥从来没有绅士过，江桥只知道：开心了就在她面前笑，不开心了就对她发脾气。",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/358847cd-2c8a-46bc-afc4-d40917657204.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 40,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "夜晚的水汽已经弄湿了这条巷子，没有人再从这里路过，只剩下头顶上的老式路灯还散发着昏黄的光线，似乎它和这条弄堂就是一对被空间隔离的恋人，每天相对却不动声色，只有当夜风吹来时，它们才会有一次擦肩而过，然后如此重复……",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/8f8b1685-c596-4dd4-9feb-8edea015af48.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 41,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "而这些关于他们寂寞的秘密，在这条弄堂里只有江桥一个人懂！",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/68c47f57-724e-4b7f-b12b-431813a1fb12.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 42,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "江桥终于回了家，木板门上挂着的铁锁用它的冰冷呼应着江桥心中的那些惆怅，连门口栽种的桂花树也不再散发芳香，只有露水依附在叶子上像个人似的仰望着清凉的月光，但空气里那些白天留下的燥热却还没有完全散去，江桥忽然发觉自己在这冷热交替的夜里有些病态了。",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/e5cd94c5-8231-4a67-8a8d-30ce47dc9237.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 43,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "江桥终于打开了门上的锁，推开了木板门，霎时惊得江桥呆立在原地……",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/8043c34f-e945-427c-b920-93d09b51f541.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 44,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "江桥看见了一个仿佛用画笔勾勒出的美丽到有些孤独的侧脸，她穿着白色的花边长裙，正拿着水壶，站在花池旁为江桥种植的那些花草浇着水，江桥不知道该怎么形容这个仿佛掉落在花前月下的身影，仅看见自己内心的寂寞只在一个星火闪过的瞬间便被点燃。",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/7354c74d-3cc5-4746-bc49-198abed852c8.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 45,
        "type": "narration",
        "role": "旁白",
        "emotion": "neutral",
        "text": "她发现了江桥，江桥也终于回过了神，几步冲刺着跑到她的面前，一把夺下了她手中的水壶，喊叫道：",
        "referenceAudio": {
          "id": "f2c00789-01a1-474d-bfcd-c5f940006be9",
          "mode": 1,
          "emoWeight": 0.65
        },
        "autoAssignedVoiceActor": null,
        "autoEmotionAudioMap": null,
        "audioUrl": "/api/tts/preview/reader_我的郁金香小姐/38d17219-2013-4cd9-9fbf-acc8d6dc9f9d.mp3"
      },
      {
        "index": 46,
        "type": "dialogue",
        "role": "江桥",
        "emotion": "angry",
